<h2 id="introduction">1. Introduction:</h2>
<p>The Enterprise Blockchain Solution developed by 10Pearls Organization is a sophisticated platform designed to empower organizations with the benefits of blockchain technology. This solution enables secure, transparent, and decentralized transactions, data management, and digital asset exchange across various industries, including finance, supply chain, healthcare, and more.</p>
<h2 id="system-requirements">2. System Requirements:</h2>
<p><strong>Hardware Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Processor: Intel Xeon or equivalent</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>RAM: 16GB or higher</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Storage: 100GB free disk space (SSD recommended)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Network: Gigabit Ethernet</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Software Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Operating System: Linux (Ubuntu 20.04 LTS recommended)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Docker Engine: Version 20.10+</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Kubernetes: Version 1.22+</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Blockchain Framework: Hyperledger Fabric 2.4+</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="installation">3. Installation:</h2>
<ol>
<li>
<p>Deploy Kubernetes cluster using preferred cloud provider or on-premises infrastructure.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Install Docker Engine and Kubernetes components on the cluster nodes.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Clone the Enterprise Blockchain Solution repository from the official 10Pearls GitHub repository.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Configure network settings, cryptographic materials, and consensus mechanisms.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Deploy the blockchain network using Kubernetes manifests or Helm charts provided.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Verify successful deployment and initialize the network.</p>
</li>
</ol>
