<h2 id="troubleshooting">6. Troubleshooting:</h2>
<p><strong>Issue:</strong> Blockchain network nodes fail to synchronize.</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Check network connectivity and peer configurations. Restart peer nodes if necessary.</p>
<p><strong>Issue:</strong> Smart contract transactions are not being committed to the ledger.</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Verify smart contract code and endorsement policies. Debug and redeploy smart contracts if needed.</p>
<h2 id="faqs">7. FAQs:</h2>
<p><strong>Q1:</strong> Is the Enterprise Blockchain Solution suitable for small-scale deployments?</p>
<p><strong>Answer:</strong> Yes, the solution is designed to scale from small-scale deployments to enterprise-grade networks, providing flexibility and scalability.</p>
<p><strong>Q2:</strong> Can the blockchain network be extended to include external participants?</p>
<p><strong>Answer:</strong> Absolutely, the solution supports consortium configurations, allowing organizations to collaborate and extend the network to external partners.</p>
